    "rowsha": "htuyRbO0i9HHV4IA+HWvsab0/KlPNS8fW72YVIvG9Bw=",
    "originContent": "**Web 界面无法访问** → 确认端口未被占用，尝试 `-p` 指定其他端口",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
